casebody.data:
DAHLSTROM v. GEMUNDER et al. (Supreme Court, Appellate Division, First Department. October 15, 1909.) Action by Carl A. Dahlstrom against August M. Gemunder and others.

With this case has been consolidated in this court, cases bearing titles as follows: People v. Eugene Shellenberg; People ex rel. James G. Collins v. John F. Ahearn, as President, et al.; Brainard T. Norris et al. v. Charles F. Hoffman et al.

No opinions. Motions granted, and questions certified as stated in orders. Orders filed.
